fe]]\n| {{Start date|2003|7|13}}\n| {{End date|2006|3}}\n| {{currency|amount=500,000|code=ARS}}\n|-\n| Santiago Del Moro\n| {{Start date|May 2020}}\n|\n| {{currency|amount=1,000,000|code=ARS}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{Flag|Armenia}}\n| {{Unbulleted list|''[[Dil kam No Dil]]''|(''{{lang|hy|\u0534\u056b\u056c \u056f\u0561\u0574 \u0546\u0578 \u0534\u056b\u056c}}'')}}\n| ?\n| [[Armenia TV]]\n| {{Start date|2006|11}}\n| {{End date|2008}}\n| {{currency|amount=50,000,000|code=AMD}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{Flag|Australia}}\n| ''[[Deal or No Deal (Australian game show)|Deal or No Deal]]''\n| [[Andrew O'Keefe]]\n| [[Seven Network]]\n| {{Start date|2003|7|13}}\n| {{End date|2013|10|4}}\n| [[Australian Dollar|AU$]]2,000,000 (2003)<br/>[[Australian Dollar|AU$]]200,000 (2004-2013)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{Flag|Austria}}\n| ''Deal or No Deal''\n| [[Rainhard Fendrich]]\n| [[ORF1]]\n| {{Start date|2005|7|1}}\n| {{End date|2005|9|2}}\n| {{currency|amount=250,000|code=EUR}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | {{Flag|Azerbaijan}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[Davam Ya Tamam]]'' \n| Idris Cafarov\n| [[Space TV]]\n| {{Start date|2010}}\n| {{End date|2011}}\n| {{currency|amount=10,000|code=AZN}}\n|-\n|[[Murad Dadashov]]\n|[[Azad Azerbaijan TV]]\n| {{Start date|2016|10|31}}\n| {{End date|2017|8|6}}\n| {{currency|amount=30,000|code=AZN}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | {{Flag|Belgium}}\n| ''[[Miljoenenjacht (Belgian game show)|Miljoenenjacht]]''\n| [[Walter Grootaers]] \n| [[Vtm]] \n| {{Start date|2004|10|16}}\n| {{End date|2005}}\n| {{currency|amount=1,000,000|code=EUR}}\n|-\n|''[[Te Nemen Of Te Laten]]''\n| [[Dr\u00e9 Steemans|Felice]]\n| [[VijfTV]]\n| {{Start date|2006|8|21}}\n| {{End date|2009}}\n| {{currency|amount=200,000|code=EUR}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{Flag|Belize}}\n| ''[[Tek It or Leave It]]''\n| [[Angela Gegg]] \n| [[Great Belize Television|Channel 5]]\n| {{Start date|2008|12|2}}\n| {{End date|2009|3|3}}\n| {{currency|amount=15,000|code=BZD}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{Flag|Braz