er' Read dies aged 95 |url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-nottinghamshire-52201667 |work= BBC News |access-date= 10 April 2020}}</ref>\n*9 April\n**[[Ida Schuster]], 101, actress (''[[Death Watch]]'', ''[[A Shot at Glory]]'').<ref>{{cite news|last1=O'Toole|first1=Emer|title=Tributes paid as world's oldest podcaster dies aged 101|url=https://www.thenational.scot/news/18371450.tributes-paid-worlds-oldest-podcaster-dies-aged-101/|work=The National|date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n**[[Dmitri Smirnov (composer)|Dmitri Smirnov]], 71, Russian-born composer (''[[Tiriel (opera)|Tiriel]]'', ''[[Thel (opera)|The Lamentations of Thel]]''), [[Coronavirus disease 2019|COVID-19]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.classicalmusicnews.ru/news/dmitrij-smirnov-passed/|title=\u0421\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0447\u0430\u043b\u0441\u044f \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u043e\u0437\u0438\u0442\u043e\u0440 \u0414\u043c\u0438\u0442\u0440\u0438\u0439 \u0421\u043c\u0438\u0440\u043d\u043e\u0432|date=9 April 2020|accessdate=9 April 2020|publisher=ClassicalMusicNews.Ru|language=ru}}</ref>\n**[[Phyllis Wallbank]], 101, educationalist.<ref>{{cite web|title=Easter Sunday Note from Parish Priest|url=http://www.littleflower.co.uk/|website=St Teresa's Catholic Church|accessdate=13 April 2020}}</ref>\n*10 April \u2013 [[Hilary Dwyer]], 74, actress (''[[Witchfinder General (1968 film)|Witchfinder General]]'', ''[[Cry of the Banshee]]'', ''[[Wuthering Heights (1970 film)|Wuthering Heights]]''), [[Coronavirus disease 2019|COVID-19]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Barnes|first=Mike|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hilary-heath-dead-actress-witchfinder-general-dies-covid-19-complications-at-74-1289887|title=Hilary Heath, Actress in 'Witchfinder General,' Dies of COVID-19 Complications at 74|work=Hollywood Reporter|date=10 April 2020}}</ref> (death announced on this date)\n*11 April \u2013 [[John Horton Conway]], 82, mathematician ([[Conway's Game of Life]], [[surreal number]]s, [[monstrous moonshine]]), [[Coronavirus di